chem.s %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = X4,
             y = Y1)) +

Binary Y1: Question 3

Y1.ind <- matrix(nrow = 20, ncol = 1)
chem$Y1.ind <- Y1.ind
for(i in 1:20){
  if(chem$Y1[i] > 100){
    chem$Y1.ind[i] = 1}
  else{
    chem$Y1.ind[i] = 0
  }
}

  ggplot(aes(x = X4, y = Y1.ind)) +
